{"tid":2487651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑臉琵鷺全球數量首破 5,000 創新高　在港持續下跌、棲息地受發展威脅","createTime":"2021-04-13T16:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T16:38:15.000Z","uid":14454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f604a103389b87ee1bf00e02bd459c63c9b0edf","tid":2487651,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme3NRQurmkpUeyTDdzzgHcxvsvRBRDeU3qxit7KKr9fmh?filename=uMYngex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMYngex.jpg&h=38d91441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBy Walter Ma<br />\n<br />\n由香港觀鳥會統籌的《黑臉琵鷺全球同步普查 2021》已於 1 月 15 至 17 日順利完成。本年度普查結果是有紀錄以來最高，全球黑臉琵鷺數量達 5,222 隻，較去年上升 7.4% ，即增加了 358 隻，再度破紀錄。然而，全球黑臉琵鷺數量大幅增加的同時，在香港棲息的黑臉琵鷺數量卻顯著下降。今年在后海灣（包括香港及深圳）錄得 336 隻，按年下跌 6.9% ，在過去 7 年間跌幅達 15% 。黑臉琵鷺的棲息地后海灣持續受發展威脅，將來或進一步惡化。<br />\n<br />\n在過去幾年，發展商多次就位於「濕地緩衝區」的發展向城規會闖關，當中包括申請放寬建築高度及密度、增加發展地積比率等。最近，政府更披露正檢討「濕地緩衝區」的規劃指引，此舉將增添發展商及土地業權人對發展的期望，增加魚塘濕地保育的難度。米埔內后海灣濕地，包括泥灘、基圍及魚塘於 1995 年正式被納入為「拉姆薩爾濕地」，具高生態及保育價值。本會促請政府為「濕地緩衝區」把關，防止發展入侵后海灣濕地，並大力推動本地塘魚養殖業，確保后海灣濕地的保育工作在生態、經濟及社會方面的可持續性；市民則可以購買來自本地魚塘的塘魚，以維持本地魚塘的競爭力。此外，政府亦應為后海灣的濕地及魚塘訂立一個長遠及整全的保育政策，包括加強由米埔延伸至下白泥沿岸淺水區及泥灘的保護，以確保每年數以萬計途經香港的候鳥們，包括全球瀕危的黑臉琵鷺，能有一個安全及食物充足的中途補給站及度冬地點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E9%BB%91%E8%87%89%E7%90%B5%E9%B7%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F%E9%A6%96%E7%A0%B4-5-000-%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E6%A3%B2%E6%81%AF%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%97%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85/?fbclid=IwAR0dpgkWSQaAAz6JmhMm8SBGgnC5lkev2HpqeKOClgJozXq360HC2jzm62A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%2587%2589%25E7%2590%25B5%25E9%25B7%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25A0%25B4-5-000-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E6%25A3%25B2%25E6%2581%25AF%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0dpgkWSQaAAz6JmhMm8SBGgnC5lkev2HpqeKOClgJozXq360HC2jzm62A&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11MLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=82712d08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%2587%2589%25E7%2590%25B5%25E9%25B7%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25A0%25B4-5-000-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E6%25A3%25B2%25E6%2581%25AF%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0dpgkWSQaAAz6JmhMm8SBGgnC5lkev2HpqeKOClgJozXq360HC2jzm62A&h=b169fc51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E9%BB%91%E8%87%89%E7%90%B5%E9%B7%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F%E9%A6%96%E7%A0%B4-5-000-%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E6%A3%B2%E6%81%AF%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%97%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85/?fbclid=IwAR0dpgkWSQaAAz6JmhMm8SBGgnC5lkev2HpqeKOClgJozXq360HC2jzm62A</a>"},{"pid":"65bed254d65c69226d16f79203f4787098ceb9c2","tid":2487651,"uid":31765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"屌，連黑臉琵鷺都移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d93fb599a9a7d5603cb6a3157e4292667f661ca","tid":2487651,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"正苦: 佢地識搬  唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcab34b04d9a555951586615cbd5574e4e83ff3a","tid":2487651,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那